      .item-text
        %h3 2015 Marketing Site
        %p In just two years from Ignite's launch, we outgrew the capabilities of what our previous one-page marketing website could provide. With a goal of raising brand awareness and increasing product adoption rate, we aimed to make more of our information and resources available online.
        %p Since this wasn't one of the organization's prioritized products, our entire design team collaborated to meet the project deadlines. My role on the team was to build a great codebase any of us could use and expand upon.
        %select.div-toggler{'data-target' => '.ignite-toggle'}
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-one', :value => 'ignite-one'} Homepage
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-two', :value => 'ignite-two'} Selfies
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-three', :value => 'ignite-three'} Jobs
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-four', :value => 'ignite-four'} Login
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-five', :value => 'ignite-five'} Resources
          %option{'data-show' => '.ignite-six', :value => 'ignite-six'} Contact
    %article.image
